# User directory — the user keeps two CSVs in the project root:
#   Users.csv               — one row per individual user / mailbox
#   DistributionLists.csv   — one row per group / distribution list
# Both are mounted into the container at /app/Users.csv and
# /app/DistributionLists.csv.  We don't commit the actual files
# (they change frequently and contain company directory data).
/Users.csv
/DistributionLists.csv

# Legacy / stray directory exports.  These used to feed the
# typeahead but have been replaced by Users.csv +
# DistributionLists.csv above.  Kept out of git so the old
# payloads (which may contain personal data) never get committed.
/users.json
/groups.json
